citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:35 AM on
24-Apr-19.
The inspector knocked on the front and side door of the residence. The inspector then called the phone number
provided. After no response, the inspector left the premise after 30 minutes.
